                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="Your Name" class="img-fluid rounded-circle">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h2>Your Name</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Network Engineering Student | Programmer | Music Composer</p>
                    <p>I'm a passionate network engineering student with a love for programming and music composition. My diverse interests allow me to bring a unique perspective to my projects and collaborations.</p>
                    
                    <h3 class="mt-4">My Interests</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Network infrastructure and security</li>
                        <li>Game development and modding</li>
                        <li>Music composition and production</li>
                        <li>Open-source software contribution</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h3 class="mt-4">Hobbies</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Playing and modding video games</li>
                        <li>Composing electronic and orchestral music</li>
                        <li>Hiking and nature photography</li>
                        <li>Reading sci-fi and technical literature</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Navigation Pills -->
        <nav class="nav nav-pills flex-column flex-sm-row">
            <a class="flex-sm-fill text-sm-center nav-link" href="#programming-projects">Programming Projects</a>
            <a class="flex-sm-fill text-sm-center nav-link" href="#music-composition">Music Composition</a>
        </nav>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

